The paper deals with problems related to graph drawing, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The use of reductions from 3-Partition suggests that the paper may also be related to computational complexity (cs.CC) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The problem of finding a simultaneous embedding of two graphs with restricted crossings is also related to the study of graph theory (cs.DS) and graph drawing algorithms (cs.GT).
